tafsir[8]{c,v,t}:
  102,1,"Soklanii mon-onon aade en- wasandirde ngalu e sukaaɓe gaa e ɗoftaade Alla."
  102,2,"Haa maayɗon naatɗon e genaale."
  102,3,"Woodanaana mon wasandirde gaa e ɗoftaade Alla, yaama nganndon batte soklirde ɗuum."
  102,4,"Refti yaama nganndon batte mum."
  102,5,"Ko goongo ma on ngaandu ganndal yananeede ko on umminteeɓe faade e Alla, ma O yoɓ mon golle mon, ko coklirɗon aduna wasandirde ngalu e sukaaɓe."
  102,6,"Wollaahi ma on ceede yiite ñanda darnga."
  102,7,"Refti ma on ceedo nge ceedagol yananeede ko aldah e sikke."
  102,8,"Refti ma Alla naamna on e oon ñalngu neema mbo O neeminno mon hono ngalu e cellal."
